---
<section class="border-b border-hairline">
  <div class="container-wide grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-2 space-y-2">
      <p class="eyebrow">Est. 2026</p>
      <p class="eyebrow">Rev. 01</p>
      <div class="hidden md:block w-8 h-[3px] bg-yellow mt-4" aria-hidden></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-10">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-6">
        <span class="text-yellow">◆</span>
        Field operations · Energy & heavy industry
      </p>
      <h1 class="display text-[clamp(3.5rem,10vw,10rem)]">
        Run the field<span class="text-yellow">.</span><br />
        <span class="text-steel">Not the paperwork<span class="text-yellow">.</span></span>
      </h1>
      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-12">
        <p class="text-lg leading-snug md:col-span-2">
          FieldOps is the operating system for NDT, inspection, crane, and industrial
          services companies — dispatch, timesheets, certifications, CRM, and
          audit-ready reports in one place. Built for teams that live on the job site.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a
            href="#demo"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-between border-2 border-ink bg-ink px-5 py-3 font-medium text-paper hover:bg-yellow hover:text-ink hover:border-yellow transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Book a demo</span>
            <span aria-hidden>→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
